{"__ud_title":"nanobot telegram sub-agents","__ud_tags":["Tools","openclaw","nanobot"],"__ud_update_time":1772938805497,"__ud_create_time":1772938803704,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"nanobot telegram sub-agents"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"在-nanobot-中为-Telegram-聊天群组频道指定专属-Agent-步骤指南"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"在 nanobot 中为 Telegram 聊天/群组/频道指定专属 Agent 步骤指南"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"目标"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"目标"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让 nanobot 在指定的 Telegram 聊天（私聊、群组或频道）中只运行一个高度专注的 Agent，专门处理特定事务（例如 RSS 摘要），不闲聊、不越界。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"步骤概览"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"步骤概览"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"创建专属工作目录"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编写行为定义文件（类似 SOUL.md）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"链接所需技能"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"创建 Agent 并设置身份"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"绑定 Telegram 聊天/群组/频道"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"重启服务并验证"}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"1-创建专属工作目录"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 创建专属工作目录"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"为专用 Agent 建立独立的工作空间，存放其人格设定和可用技能。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bash"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"mkdir -p ~/.nanobot/workspace-rss/skills"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"将 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"workspace-rss"},{"type":"text","text":" 替换为实际用途的名称，例如 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"workspace-weather"},{"type":"text","text":"。"}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"2-定义行为边界核心"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 定义行为边界（核心）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"workspace-rss"},{"type":"text","text":" 目录下创建 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"SOUL.md"},{"type":"text","text":"（或其他 nanobot 规定的行为配置文件），明确 Agent 的职责和限制。"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"示例 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"SOUL.md"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"markdown"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - RSS 摘要专用 Agent\n\n## 核心原则\n你是一个 RSS 内容摘要助手。唯一职责是按照用户要求，使用 `miniflux-reader` 技能获取和总结 Miniflux 中的订阅内容。\n\n## 行为规则\n- **严格执行**：用户要求总结几条就几条，指定哪个 feed/category 就总结哪个。\n- **不扩展**：不主动添加用户未要求的内容。\n- **不闲聊**：不寒暄、不发表与 RSS 无关的评论。\n- **标记已读**：仅在用户明确要求“总结新的”时，才将上一轮总结过的条目标记为已读；仅查询时不标记。\n\n## 边界\n- 拒绝处理与 RSS/Feed 无关的请求，礼貌说明只负责 RSS 内容摘要。"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通过明确“不做什么”让 Agent 保持专注。"}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"3-链接所需技能"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 链接所需技能"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"将需要用到的技能软链接到工作区的 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"skills"},{"type":"text","text":" 目录。假设技能仓库在 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"~/.nanobot/skills/"},{"type":"text","text":"。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bash"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ln -s ~/.nanobot/skills/miniflux-reader ~/.nanobot/workspace-rss/skills/miniflux-reader"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"软链接便于技能更新时自动同步。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如需多个技能，依次链接。"}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"4-创建-Agent-并设置身份"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. 创建 Agent 并设置身份"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用 nanobot 命令行工具创建 Agent，指定工作区和模型。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bash"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"nanobot agents add rss \\\n  --workspace ~/.nanobot/workspace-rss \\\n  --model your-preferred-model  # 例如 openai/gpt-4, claude-3 等"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"然后设置身份（名称和表情符号）："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bash"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"nanobot agents set-identity --agent rss --name \"RSS 助手\" --emoji \"📰\""}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"身份信息会显示在回复中，方便区分是哪个 Agent 在响应。"}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"5-绑定-Telegram-聊天群组频道"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. 绑定 Telegram 聊天/群组/频道"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编辑 nanobot 的主配置文件（通常为 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"~/.nanobot/nanobot.json"},{"type":"text","text":"），在 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"bindings"},{"type":"text","text":" 数组中添加一条路由规则，将特定 Telegram 实体的消息指向刚创建的 Agent。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"获取 Telegram 聊天/群组/频道 ID"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"向 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"@getidsbot"},{"type":"text","text":" 发送任意消息，它会返回当前聊天的 ID 等信息。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"或者在群组/频道中，将机器人添加为管理员，然后通过机器人 API 获取更新中的 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"chat.id"},{"type":"text","text":"。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"示例配置片段"},{"type":"text","text":"（假设 nanobot 使用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"channel\": \"telegram\""},{"type":"text","text":" 标识平台）："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"json"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"bindings\": [\n    // 其他绑定规则...\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"rss\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"peer\": {\n          \"kind\": \"chat\",        // 可选值：chat（私聊）、group、channel\n          \"id\": 123456789        // 替换为你的聊天/群组/频道 ID（整数）\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"私聊"},{"type":"text","text":"："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"kind\": \"chat\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"群组"},{"type":"text","text":"："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"kind\": \"group\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"频道"},{"type":"text","text":"："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"kind\": \"channel\""}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果 nanobot 支持按整个群组/频道路由而不区分具体 ID，可能还有 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"groupId"},{"type":"text","text":"、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"channelId"},{"type":"text","text":" 字段，请根据实际文档调整。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"路由匹配维度参考"},{"type":"text","text":"（根据 nanobot 实际支持情况调整）："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"字段用途"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"peer.kind"},{"type":"text","text":" + "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"id"},{"type":"text","text":"匹配特定私聊、群组或频道"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"chatId"},{"type":"text","text":"匹配所有来自该 ID 的聊天（简写）"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"accountId"},{"type":"text","text":"匹配特定 Telegram 账号（多账号场景）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"保存文件后，重启 nanobot 的网关服务以使配置生效："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bash"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"nanobot gateway restart"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"6-验证"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. 验证"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在绑定的 Telegram 聊天中发送一条简单消息，例如“你是谁”。"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果回复中包含你设置的身份（名称或表情符号），说明路由成功。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"也可以尝试发一条 RSS 摘要指令，观察是否只调用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"miniflux-reader"},{"type":"text","text":" 技能且不闲聊。"}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"注意事项"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"注意事项"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"备份配置"},{"type":"text","text":"：修改 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"nanobot.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 前建议备份原文件。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"模型选择"},{"type":"text","text":"：专用 Agent 可使用较小或成本较低的模型，因为任务单一。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"技能路径"},{"type":"text","text":"：根据你的技能安装位置调整软链接命令。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"多 Agent 共存"},{"type":"text","text":"：可以创建多个专用 Agent，通过不同的路由规则分配到不同的 Telegram 聊天。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通过以上步骤，你就能在 nanobot 中为 Telegram 实现专属 Agent，让每个聊天拥有一个高度专注的助手。"}]}]}